&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead high performance technology teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead from the front and lead by example&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hire &amp;amp; develop talented leads &amp;amp; engineers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and drive business features into technology requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Product Managers, Customers to align technology choices with business requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure high quality and timely release &amp;amp; support of products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively drive and contribute to architecture and design of products and APIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay updated on emerging technologies and apply them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a catalyst and drive continuous improvement of engineering practices and improve enginee

&lt;p&gt;Role: Finance Executive, Greater China&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reports to: Finance Manager, Greater China&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Location: Hongkong&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;THE OPPORTUNITY&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here&#39;s an exciting chance to join a global firm with a matching global culture. At MiQ, we embody our values to help businesses succeed and support our employees&#39; growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MiQ is a world - leading programmatic ads company, headquartered in London and New York, operating in over 10 countries for top - tier media buy clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MiQ China was set up in 2020 and now has offices in Beijing, Shanghai, Guangzhou, and Hongkong, focusing on China&#39;s outbound advertising to help clients succeed overseas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role acts as a bridge between the UK and China finance teams, this role will be responsible for delivering financial operational services to Hong Kong companies and supporting China offshore business. Reporting directly to the Finance Manager, the role demands a solid foundation in financial expertise, exceptional communication abilities, and proficiency in working both independently and collaboratively within a team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;JOB RESPONSIBILITITES&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your main responsibilities will include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Financial Reporting &amp;amp; Compliance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with UK Central Finance and China Mainland Finance teams to prepare accurate and timely monthly financial statements for the Hong Kong entity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the month-end closing process, the year-end tax filing and financial audits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Company Secretarial &amp;amp; Payments&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the company secretarial functions for the Hong Kong company, including maintaining statutory records and ensuring compliance with local regulations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review and apply for the company payment requests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Outbound Business Support&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle invoicing and payment tracking for China outbound business, ensuring timely and accurate processing of transactions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;China Payment Support&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist the mainland China finance team with payment application&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ad-hoc Support&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide support on other finance-related or administrative/HR tasks as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE/QUALIFICATIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in accounting or finance. A professional accounting qualification (e.g., CPA, ACCA) is highly preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2-3+ years of relevant experience in a similar role, preferably generalist in small and medium sized companies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of Hong Kong Financial Reporting Standards (HKFRS) and local accounting regulations&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with company secretarial functions is essential&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills in English and Cantonese; Mandarin is a plus&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical and problem-solving skills with meticulous attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
