&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Title:&lt;/strong&gt; Programmatic Advertising Business Development Manager&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Beijing, Shanghai, Guangzhou, or Shenzhen&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Company:&lt;/strong&gt; MiQ&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Department:&lt;/strong&gt; Sales &amp;amp; Business Development&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About MiQ&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MiQ is a leading global programmatic advertising technology company, specialising in leveraging data science and analytics to deliver intelligent marketing solutions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Founded in 2010 and headquartered in London, MiQ operates in multiple markets worldwide. Since entering China in 2020, MiQ has been dedicated to supporting Chinese brands in their international expansion, enabling efficient media investment and sustainable business growth.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MiQ China Outbound team leverages leading platforms such as DV360, Amazon DSP and other global technologies, combined with proprietary data and analytics, to deliver full-funnel programmatic marketing solutions&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Overview&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will take charge of developing and expanding MiQ&#39;s programmatic advertising business in the auto, finance, and travel industries for China outbound (Export) business. You will be responsible for building deep cooperative relationships with key clients and agencies in these sectors, formulating targeted sales strategies, and achieving revenue targets while enhancing MiQ&#39;s brand influence in these vertical fields.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;Business Development &amp;amp; Client Expansion&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively develop new clients in the auto, finance, and travel industries. At the same time, maintain and deepen partnerships with existing key clients to promote continuous business growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Revenue Target Achievement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set reasonable monthly, quarterly, and annual sales targets based on MiQ&#39;s business development strategy and the market characteristics of the auto, finance, and travel industries. And formulate actionable sales plans to ensure the successful achievement of these revenue goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Industry Expertise &amp;amp; Brand Promotion&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Act as an evangelist for programmatic advertising in the verticals.&amp;nbsp; Organize industry workshops, product demonstrations, and case sharing sessions regularly. Educate clients on the value of programmatic advertising in scenarios like precision user positioning for new car releases, risk - controlled promotion of financial products, and customized marketing for travel routes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep a close eye on industry trends, such as the application of programmatic advertising in new energy vehicle marketing and the compliance requirements of financial advertising. Then combine MiQ&#39;s technical advantages to highlight the company&#39;s competitive edges to clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Team Collaboration &amp;amp; Solution Optimization&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with internal teams including Client Services, Trading, and Data Analytics. Ensure the smooth implementation of client advertising campaigns and timely optimize strategies according to data feedback to improve campaign effects.&lt;/li&gt;
